HEADWORD: Lowlander
<hw>Low"land*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A native or
inhabitant of the Lowlands, especially of the Lowlands of Scotland, as
distinguished from <contr>Highlander</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
